The Aggie Hosts, a student policing program, provides a free Campus Escort Service.  To use this service call 752-1727.

This free service provides safety escorts to UC Davis students, staff, faculty, and visitors between ["Campus"] locations and nearby residential areas.  They drive white vans and glare at harmless guys whom they chance to see walking around campus.

The ["Campus Safety"] Escort Service operates 365 days a year.  Hours of operation are:

6:00pm - 12:00am during the academic year.
6:00pm - 1:00am during ["Finals" finals] week.
8:00pm - 12:00am during summer session.

